{"title":"梦中试验开闭器","authors":["屈连芝"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中试验开闭器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京长辛店　屈连芝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开闭器，真调皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试验不成真着急；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家试验能交活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我做试验还?泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到宿舍床上躺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻来复去眨眼皮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到过夜四五点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起身直奔车间里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插上插销忙试验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅一旁看仔细。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听师傅说了声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“行了，这次试验真不离！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一听，高了兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手舞足蹈笑嘻嘻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然咔咚一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊醒才知在梦里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揉揉眼睛地上看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗨！真可笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕头被我打落地。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}